    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Washed ashore, stripped bare, and abandoned. You were meant to die on that prison ship. But fate, in its cruelest irony, has delivered you to this island—a place where death is everyone's mutual companion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 days. 100 days until a faint beacon of hope arrives. 100 days to survive a relentless onslaught of monstrous creatures that emerge from the island's depths. 100 days to unravel the secrets of this cursed land. Survival means evolution, especially when every sunrise could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393180/extras/355d22f4b611f8d1df528dbc49d26abf.avif?t=1744845600\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393180/extras_big/355d22f4b611f8d1df528dbc49d26abf.avif?t=1744845600 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploit EVERY Resource:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the skeletal remains of shipwrecks to veins of ore, every resource is a weapon against oblivion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Construct Your SANCTUARY:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than a shelter—forge a fortress against the nightmares that stalk the night. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt or PERISH:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft weapons, forge armor, and master magic to stand against the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
